# Zelta Theme Pack

Community Slack and terminal themes inspired by zelta.space - perfect backups, powered by ZFS.

Free theme pack inspired by Zelta, the open-source ZFS backup suite by Bell Tower. 

## Slack Themes

Go to **Preferences > Themes > Custom theme > Import** and paste a string.

